creator: Auto1.com
descriptionHtml:
THE FUTURE OF VEHICLE EVALUATIONS

AUTO1 EVA allows you to sell cars to more than 60.000 car dealers in over 30 countries.

Benefit from competitive European prices while interacting with and selling to one contract partner only. AUTO1.com handles the full process for you including payment, transport and export handling.

With this brand new app, you can sell trade-ins quicker and easier than ever.

HOW DOES AUTO1 EVA WORK?
Evaluate a car with our intuitive step-by-step guide in under 15 minutes
Import DAT data automatically and fill in remaining car details manually via the app
After the evaluation, you can start selling your car to 60.000 dealers on AUTO1.com with your expected price

KEY APP FEATURES
Step-by-Step Evaluation Process - Don’t miss to document a single part of the car
Equipment automatically pulled based on VIN
Guided photo taking
Structured Test Drive Documentation
Document wheels, documents and service details


WHY YOU SHOULD USE AUTO1 EVA
Shorter evaluation time with state-of-the-art usability
Document the full car in under 15 minutes and directly sell with one fingertip
Cross-device interaction: Start the evaluation on your desktop and finish on your mobile phone
Flexible evaluation with option to save progress and complete later
Fully structured process that guides you through the evaluation

WHY CHOOSE REMARKETING WITH AUTO1.COM?
AUTO1.com creates competition by selling to more than 60.000 dealers from 30 countries leading to best-in-class prices for our sellers
Sell cars within 24 hours through our digital auction
AUTO1.com handles the full process including payment, document handling and transport.

OUR SERVICES
Monitor and control all interactions in your Remarketing Dashboard on AUTO1.com
We provide a seamless integration to your system via REST API
Our Price Indicator tool for Trade-Ins provides you with real time prices based on 2 million transactions
We offer tailored logistic solutions through our extensive partner network


GET IN TOUCH
If you have any questions, please don’t hesitate to contact us directly via email remarketing-info@auto1.com, or by phone on +49 030 2647 5154.
